des:
'My Biorhythms' calculates all the quotients from your biorhythm cycles. 

The basic version gives you a daily reading of your primary quotients: Physical, Emotional, and Intellectual. 

You can also subscribe to the complete version within the skill. The complete version also calculates your Intuition/Compassion Biorhythm Quotient, Aesthetic Biorhythm Quotient, Self Awareness Biorhythm Quotient, and Spiritual Biorhythm Quotient.

The readings vary from -100 to +100, where -100 is least efficient, 0 is neutral and +100 is most efficient.

The skill will also tell you if your specific quotient is on the rise or decline. In the complete version, the 'My Biorhythms' skill will give you tips to make the best out of your day!
